title: Elf Dark Skin Tone
description: A fantastical creature with pointed ears, often associated with magic and folklore. This version has a dark skin tone.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the elf with dark skin tone is illustrated with a playful and whimsical charm, featuring pointed ears and a distinctly magical aura. Its design on Apple devices utilizes smooth gradients and subtle, realistic lighting to give it an enchanting, almost storybook quality. This emoji embodies fantasy, mischief, and the extraordinary, perfect for adding a touch of wonder to digital conversations.
